Package org.spongepowered.api.map.decoration.orientation

Class MapDecorationOrientations

java.lang.Object
org.spongepowered.api.map.decoration.orientation.MapDecorationOrientations
public class MapDecorationOrientations extends Object
A pseudo-enum of supported orientations of a MapDecoration The NORTH orientation is the upwards orientation on a map.
